---
title: Veggie Fattoush Salad with Crispy Chickpeas and Garlic Oil
description: It doesn’t matter if your favorite part of salad is the fresh veggies or the crispy croutons: fattoush will satisfy either way. The Lebanese dish features a jumble of greens, cucumbers, tomatoes, and chickpeas along with chunks of toasted bread. We’ll be using pieces of pita here, which soak up the dressing and have a dusting of herby za’atar for plenty of vibrant flavor.
